   value = a.mat;
   n=1;
$gameParty.members().forEach( function(valor, indice, array) {
    if($gameParty.members()[indice].hasState(11))
      n+=1;
});
$gameTroop.members().forEach( function(valor, indice, array) {

      n+=1;
});
